flowchart TD
    A[TLB Miss] --> B[Hardware page table walk]
    B --> C{PTE valid?}
    C -->|yes| D[Load TLB entry]
    C -->|no| E[Page fault exception]
    E --> F[as_fault handles miss]
    F --> G[Segment driver loads page]
    G --> H[hat_memload creates mapping]
    H --> I[Return to faulting instruction]
